  A few simple steps are needed to compile the program:

 (1) cd to directory "source": >cd source
 (2) copy the appropriate Makefile.machine to Makefile (or edit the Makefile)
 (3) type >make
 (4) move the libatom.a to parent directory: >mv libatom.a ..
 (5) go back to the parent directory: >cd ..
 (6) Use TO_COMPILE.machine to compile the .exe files: > ./TO_COMPILE.machine
     There should result in the following files:
     atom.exe, atomkb.exe,conv_plot.exe,conv_plot_kb.exe,
     gen_vwr.exe, kbconv.exe,lnplot.exe,lnplot_kb.exe
 (7) You are done !
